Subject: [PATCH] thumbcache: Add new dll

---
 configure.ac                       |  1 +
 dlls/thumbcache/Makefile.in        |  5 ++++
 dlls/thumbcache/thumbcache.c       | 33 ++++++++++++++++++++++++
